  "detailed_description": "<h1>WISHLIST & JOIN US ON DISCORD</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/f0ac9333af382d378f92ec51ed702f68.apng?t=1739922536\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/f0ac9333af382d378f92ec51ed702f68.poster.avif?t=1739922536\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=196 /></picture></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/e077c3d3f87eb7bb7f3d31e751f6d7b1.apng?t=1739922536\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/e077c3d3f87eb7bb7f3d31e751f6d7b1.poster.avif?t=1739922536\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=196 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mechanines Tower Defense</strong> is a strategy game that combines rogue-lite elements with the dynamic of tower defense, offering a unique experience with every match. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlike traditional titles, enemy paths are procedurally generated and infinite, ensuring no session is the same. In addition, EvoDog placement points are random, challenging players to adapt their strategies in real-time. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategy and Resistance</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/f45b3fc0f5481df338beedfad7adaf31.poster.avif?t=1739922536\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/f45b3fc0f5481df338beedfad7adaf31.webm?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/f45b3fc0f5481df338beedfad7adaf31.mp4?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each match presents new challenges with maps that expand as you progress. The key to success is using the unique abilities of the EvoDogs and leveraging the procedural terrain expansion to create effective defenses. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Positioning and EvoDogs</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/1da74dd31dbde9a4114c2f90f1dfbd5b.poster.avif?t=1739922536\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/1da74dd31dbde9a4114c2f90f1dfbd5b.webm?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from various types of EvoDogs, each with unique abilities, and place them in strategic locations, influencing their performance by increasing attack power, endurance, or tactical support in protecting the PetLab. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DogCoins and Abilities</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/1df411613e29794c99e084997abb9d44.poster.avif?t=1739922536\" width=800 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/1df411613e29794c99e084997abb9d44.webm?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/1df411613e29794c99e084997abb9d44.mp4?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use DogCoins to evolve your EvoDogs and unlock permanent upgrades at the PetLab, unlocking new abilities and strengthening your defense team to face tougher waves of Mechanoids. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Global Competition</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/28d719863d5b34b4999d6df3154ba6a2.poster.avif?t=1739922536\" width=800 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/28d719863d5b34b4999d6df3154ba6a2.webm?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/28d719863d5b34b4999d6df3154ba6a2.mp4?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put your skills to the test by competing globally or with friends, aiming for the highest score and proving who is the best commander. Prepare for an epic battle where the loyalty and bravery of our best friends can change humanity's fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>It's not about winning, but about not giving up.</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/e077c3d3f87eb7bb7f3d31e751f6d7b1.apng?t=1739922536\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/e077c3d3f87eb7bb7f3d31e751f6d7b1.poster.avif?t=1739922536\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=196 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mechanines Tower Defense</strong> is a strategy game that combines rogue-lite elements with the dynamic of tower defense, offering a unique experience with every match. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlike traditional titles, enemy paths are procedurally generated and infinite, ensuring no session is the same. In addition, EvoDog placement points are random, challenging players to adapt their strategies in real-time. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategy and Resistance</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/f45b3fc0f5481df338beedfad7adaf31.poster.avif?t=1739922536\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/f45b3fc0f5481df338beedfad7adaf31.webm?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/f45b3fc0f5481df338beedfad7adaf31.mp4?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each match presents new challenges with maps that expand as you progress. The key to success is using the unique abilities of the EvoDogs and leveraging the procedural terrain expansion to create effective defenses. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Positioning and EvoDogs</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/1da74dd31dbde9a4114c2f90f1dfbd5b.poster.avif?t=1739922536\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/1da74dd31dbde9a4114c2f90f1dfbd5b.webm?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from various types of EvoDogs, each with unique abilities, and place them in strategic locations, influencing their performance by increasing attack power, endurance, or tactical support in protecting the PetLab. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DogCoins and Abilities</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/1df411613e29794c99e084997abb9d44.poster.avif?t=1739922536\" width=800 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/1df411613e29794c99e084997abb9d44.webm?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/1df411613e29794c99e084997abb9d44.mp4?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use DogCoins to evolve your EvoDogs and unlock permanent upgrades at the PetLab, unlocking new abilities and strengthening your defense team to face tougher waves of Mechanoids. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Global Competition</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/28d719863d5b34b4999d6df3154ba6a2.poster.avif?t=1739922536\" width=800 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/28d719863d5b34b4999d6df3154ba6a2.webm?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095890/extras/28d719863d5b34b4999d6df3154ba6a2.mp4?t=1739922536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put your skills to the test by competing globally or with friends, aiming for the highest score and proving who is the best commander. Prepare for an epic battle where the loyalty and bravery of our best friends can change humanity's fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>It's not about winning, but about not giving up.</i></p>",
